rows.label: qst105601_msg001
rows.name: やあ　先生久しぶり！

rows.label: qst105601_msg002
rows.name:
ルクスリアがアデルの正当な後継でない事に
納得がいかない

rows.label: qst105601_msg0001
rows.name: *sigh*

rows.label: qst105601_msg0002
rows.name:
Master Liberbrant! Haven't seen you
in donkey's!

rows.label: qst105601_msg0003
rows.name:
Hmm? Oh! Your Highness?!
I'm so sorry, I didn't recognize you!

rows.label: qst105601_msg0004
rows.name:
Well met, well met indeed!
And good to see you too, Saika!
You both look the picture of health!

rows.label: qst105601_msg0005
rows.name:
Nice to see you too, Master Liberbrant!
You're lookin' chirpy as ever!

rows.label: qst105601_msg0006
rows.name:
This gentleman here took care of
the prince when he was a kid.

rows.label: qst105601_msg0007
rows.name: Yep. I owe a lot to this chap.

rows.label: qst105601_msg0008
rows.name: So Master, what's with the sighing?

rows.label: qst105601_msg0009
rows.name:
Oh, it's nothing you need concern
yourself with. I would hate to be
wasting your time.

rows.label: qst105601_msg0010
rows.name:
Now don't be like that. You're not
exactly being very convincing.

rows.label: qst105601_msg0011
rows.name:
You're not wasting anyone's time.
Come on, spit it out.

rows.label: qst105601_msg0012
rows.name: Hmm. Well, then...

rows.label: qst105601_msg0013
rows.name:
I'm afraid this may seem a mite
unsavory to be discussing with
you...

rows.label: qst105601_msg0014
rows.name:
It's about the king. There are some
who dispute his claim to the throne.
That he is not Adel's heir.

rows.label: qst105601_msg0015
rows.name:
Is it true? Does the king... Does Your
Highness not share Adel's blood?

rows.label: qst105601_msg0016
rows.name: It's true. Bloody shame, though.

rows.label: qst105601_msg0017
rows.name:
T-that cannot be! Then the retainers,
the people... They have all been
deceived? This whole time?

rows.label: qst105601_msg0018
rows.name:
This is unthinkable! I had such respect
for the king, and for his ancestors...

rows.label: qst105601_msg0019
rows.name:
No. No, in the end, it is all rumor and
gossip. Someone must have planted
false information, and...

rows.label: qst105601_msg0020
rows.name:
Master Liberbrant, I'm sorry.
It's not a rumor.

rows.label: qst105601_msg0021
rows.name: But...

rows.label: qst105601_msg0022
rows.name:
I know how important empirical proof
is for you, Master.

rows.label: qst105601_msg0023
rows.name:
Always telling me not to believe
anything you haven't seen for yourself.
You drilled that into me, that's for sure.

rows.label: qst105601_msg0024
rows.name:
Just you wait and see. Let me go and
have a quick chat with my old man.

rows.label: qst105601_msg0025
rows.name: What are you planning, My Prince?

rows.label: qst105601_msg0026
rows.name: Remember that room he showed us?

rows.label: qst105601_msg0027
rows.name:
It was chock full of ornaments and
decorations. There's got to be some
sort of written statement in there.

rows.label: qst105601_msg0028
rows.name:
Are you sure about this? It's going to
'cos one hell of an uproar.

rows.label: qst105601_msg0029
rows.name:
I couldn't care less. What's the
point hiding it now anyway?

rows.label: qst105601_msg0030
rows.name:
It might be hard on you, Master
Liberbrant, but you've got to come to
terms with it one way or another,okay?

rows.label: qst105601_msg0031
rows.name: ...As you wish, Your Highness.

rows.label: qst105601_msg0032
rows.name:
Well then, time to pay my old man
a visit!
